  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of CHF 5259 (glycopyrrolate
      bromide) for the treatment of COPD patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A Multinational, Multicentre, Randomised, Double Blind, Placebo-Controlled, 2-way Crossover
      Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Glycopyrrolate Bromide Administered Via pMDI
      (CHF 5259), for the Treatment of Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
